There are multiple factors to consider when determining the correct size for crown moulding. For crown moulding, choosing the correct size may depend on several factors:

The size and shape of the crown moulding;
Degrees of coverage where the stone from the base of the crown moulding is exposed;
Durable grain size of the crown moulding which can fit bags, chins and many other items;
The amount of overlap between the stone in the base and the crown moulding where there is a large amount of break in the dust covering between the base of the crown moulding and the arch;
